result.title: Starting ACM-ICPC at my college.
result.content: Hello, I'm a freshman at my college in the USA and we don't have a ACM-ICPC team. I want to start a club for it and I'm talking with professors and other organizations to see who wants to support me. I think I'm going to start a meeting with people that are interested this week and explain what ICPC is. I'm not really sure on how to get it started. Any tips?
